Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements

Class CertificationElement

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.RelatedMetadataElementSummary
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.metadataelements.CertificationElement
public class CertificationElement extends RelatedMetadataElementSummary
CertificationElement contains the properties and header for a certification for an element. It includes the details of the specific element's certification and details of the certification type.
